- **Documentation** — `.agent/messages/documentation.md` when you solve a non-trivial problem

## Message Protocol

When writing to another agent's inbox, append using this format (see `.agent/README.md`):

```markdown
---
from: {{file}}
to: <agent-file>
date: <ISO-8601>
subject: <short title>
---

<body>
```

## Troubleshooting Protocol

When you solve a problem in your domain, write to `.agent/messages/documentation.md`:

```
**Domain**: {{roleName}}
**Problem**: <title>
**Symptom**: <what went wrong>
**Root Cause**: <why>
**Solution**: <steps>
**References**: <PR #, file:line>
```

## Tone

Professional, concise, and action-oriented. Flag risks early; do not bury blockers.
